      "span_text": "The MCE of F. benghalensis contains glycoside; 20-tetratriaconthene-2-one, 6-heptatriacontene-10-one, pentatriacontan-5-one, beta sitosterol-alpha-D-glucose and meso-inositol have been isolated from the bark  ."
